                explains their origins and the reasons why they create the wonderful items they
                do.
            </p>
            <p class="more">
                <a href="#">More</a></p>
            <h1>
                <em>Fair Trade</em></h1>
            <p>
                <em>Fashinon</em> is a fair trade partner and we ensure that we only buy from small
                traders and co-operatives
            </p>
            <p class="more">
                <a href="#">More</a></p>
        </div>
           <div class="sideBox slot one" style="margin-left: 10px;">
